<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ARDIRE Capital | Estruturação Financeira e Ativos de Crédito</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #061626;
      --navy2: #0a2238;
      --gold: #d5ad55;
      --gold2: #f0d489;
      --muted: #cbd5e1;
      --light: #f6f8fb;
      --dark: #020812;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,.13);
      --shadow: 0 22px 55px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: white;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .container {
      width: min(1180px, 92%);
      margin: auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 999;
      background: rgba(7,21,38,.94);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav {
      height: 78px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .brand-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-width: 170px;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .brand-logo-img {
      max-height: 44px;
      max-width: 210px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .brand-logo-text {
      display: none;
      font-family: "Montserrat", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .brand-logo-text strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: #f8fafc;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .brand-logo-text span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 5px;
      font-size: .58rem;
      letter-spacing: 7px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .menu {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    .menu a {
      font-size: .92rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      transition: .25s;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-transform: none;
    }

    .menu a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

    .nav-dropdown {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }

    .nav-dropdown::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: -12px;
      right: -12px;
      top: 100%;
      height: 14px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-toggle {
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: .25s;
      padding: 0;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      text-transform: none;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-toggle:hover {
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu {
      position: absolute;
      top: calc(100% + 10px);
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px);
      min-width: 300px;
      max-width: 360px;
      background: rgba(7,21,38,.98);
      border: 1px solid rgba(213,173,85,.38);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: .25s ease;
      max-height: 370px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .nav-dropdown:hover > .nav-dropdown-menu {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
      pointer-events: auto;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu a {
      display: block;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.32;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu a:hover {
      background: rgba(213,173,85,.12);
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 6px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: rgba(213,173,85,.55);
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .nav-btn {
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold) !important;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .hamburger {
      display: none;
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding-top: 120px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 72% 28%, rgba(213,173,85,.13), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #061626 0%, #071f34 52%, #0a2238 100%);
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 54px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-brand-lockup {
      display: inline-block;
      width: auto;
      max-width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
      font-family: "Montserrat", "Gotham", "Proxima Nova", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .hero-ardire {
      display: block;
      width: max-content;
      font-size: 96px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 0.85;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #f8fafc;
      background: none;
      -webkit-background-clip: initial;
      background-clip: initial;
      text-shadow: none;
    }

    .hero-capital {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 38px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      background: none;
      -webkit-background-clip: initial;
      background-clip: initial;
      text-shadow: none;
    }

    .hero-capital span {
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      margin-top: 38px;
      font-size: 21px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #c7a46b;
      text-shadow:
        1px 1px 0 rgba(243,215,138,.45),
        3px 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.72);
    }

    .hero p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.12rem;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: .25s;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold2));
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.22);
    }

    .video-frame {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 420px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 0;
      background: var(--navy);
      border: none;
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .video-frame video {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      object-position: center center;
      display: block;
      background: var(--navy);
    }

    .video-frame::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        rgba(7,21,38,.55),
        rgba(7,21,38,.15),
        rgba(7,21,38,.55)
      );
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    section {
      padding: 92px 0;
      scroll-margin-top: 90px;
    }

    .section-light {
      background: var(--light);
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .section-dark {
      background: var(--navy);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      color: var(--gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section-title {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin-bottom: 42px;
    }

    .section-title h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.05rem);
      line-height: 1.12;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section-title p {
      opacity: .78;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 30px;
      transition: .25s;
      display: block;
    }

    .section-light .card {
      background: white;
      color: var(--navy);
      border: 1px solid rgba(7,21,38,.09);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(7,21,38,.08);
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: rgba(213,173,85,.5);
    }

    .icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(213,173,85,.14);
      color: var(--gold);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .98rem;
    }

    .section-light .card p {
      color: #475569;
    }

    .solution-link {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 42px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-image {
      min-height: 430px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(6,22,38,.12), rgba(6,22,38,.36)),
        url("ardire-securitizacao-hero.png")
        center/cover no-repeat;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .text p {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      opacity: .82;
    }

    .product-page {
      padding: 86px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }

    .product-box {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: .75fr 1.25fr;
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: start;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.045);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .product-box h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .product-box p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .product-box ul {
      color: var(--muted);
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .product-box li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .governance {
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(7,21,38,.94), rgba(7,21,38,.97)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80")
        center/cover no-repeat;
    }

    .contact-box {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    form {
      background: white;
      color: var(--navy);
      padding: 34px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(7,21,38,.12);
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 7px;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }

    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(7,21,38,.18);
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 17px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      outline: none;
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 130px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    input:focus, textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--gold);
    }

    .contact-info {
      background: var(--navy2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 34px;
    }

    .contact-info h3 {
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .contact-info p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .socials {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .socials a {
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }

    footer {
      background: var(--dark);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 50px 0 26px;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    footer h3, footer h4 {
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    footer p, footer a {
      color: var(--muted);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: .94rem;
    }

    .copy {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .84rem;
    }

    .whatsapp-float {
      position: fixed;
      right: 22px;
      bottom: 22px;
      width: 58px;
      height: 58px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #25d366;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      z-index: 998;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: .7s ease;
    }

    .reveal.active {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }



    .product-intro {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
    }

    .product-block {
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }

    .product-block strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: .78rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.4px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .product-block p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    @media (min-width: 981px) {
      .nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-toggle { color: var(--muted); }

      .nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
        opacity: 0 !important;
        visibility: hidden !important;
        pointer-events: none !important;
        transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px) !important;
      }

      .nav-dropdown:hover .nav-dropdown-toggle { color: var(--gold); }

      .nav-dropdown:hover > .nav-dropdown-menu {
        opacity: 1 !important;
        visibility: visible !important;
        pointer-events: auto !important;
        transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0) !important;
      }
    }

    .whatsapp-float img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      display: block;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hamburger {
        display: block;
      }

      .nav {
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .brand-top {
        min-width: auto;
      }

      .brand-logo-img {
        max-height: 38px;
        max-width: 180px;
      }

      .menu {
        position: fixed;
        top: 78px;
        right: -100%;
        width: 84%;
        height: calc(100vh - 78px);
        background: var(--navy2);
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 32px;
        transition: .3s;
        border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .menu.active {
        right: 0;
      }

      .nav-dropdown {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
      }

      .nav-dropdown-toggle {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: left;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: .92rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .nav-dropdown-menu {
        position: static;
        transform: none;
        width: 100%;
        min-width: 0;
        max-height: 260px;
        margin-top: 14px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.035);
        opacity: 1;
        visibility: visible;
        pointer-events: auto;
        box-shadow: none;
        display: none;
      }

      .nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-toggle {
        color: var(--gold);
      }

      .nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
        display: block;
        transform: none;
      }

      .nav-dropdown:hover .nav-dropdown-menu {
        transform: none;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .about-grid,
      .grid-2,
      .contact-box,
      .footer-grid,
      .product-box {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: auto;
        padding: 130px 0 78px;
      }

      .video-frame {
        height: 300px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .hero-ardire {
        font-size: 54px;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
      }

      .hero-capital {
        font-size: 22px;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 13px;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        margin-top: 26px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .nav {
        height: 70px;
      }

      .menu {
        top: 70px;
        height: calc(100vh - 70px);
      }

      .grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      section {
        padding: 70px 0;
      }

      .product-page {
        padding: 56px 0;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .video-frame {
        height: 240px;
      }

      .whatsapp-float {
        width: 54px;
        height: 54px;
        right: 16px;
        bottom: 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header class="topbar">
  <div class="container nav">
    <a href="#inicio" class="brand-top" aria-label="ARDIRE Capital">
      <img src="logo-ardire.png" alt="ARDIRE Capital" class="brand-logo-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
      <span class="brand-logo-text"><strong>ARDIRE</strong><span>CAPITAL</span></span>
    </a>

    <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger">☰</button>

    <nav class="menu" id="menu">
      <a href="#inicio">Início</a>
      <a href="#sobre">Sobre</a>

      <div class="nav-dropdown">
        <button class="nav-dropdown-toggle" type="button">Soluções</button>
        <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
          <a href="#produtos">Visão geral das soluções</a>
          <a href="#para-empresas">Para empresas</a>
          <a href="#para-pessoas">Para pessoas</a>
          <a href="#produto-garantia-locaticia">Garantias</a>
          <a href="#investidores">Investidores</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="nav-dropdown">
        <button class="nav-dropdown-toggle" type="button">Para Empresas</button>
        <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
          <a href="#produto-recebiveis">Recebíveis</a>
          <a href="#produto-capital-giro">Capital de Giro Estruturado</a>
          <a href="#produto-antecipacoes">Antecipações</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="nav-dropdown">
        <button class="nav-dropdown-toggle" type="button">Para Pessoas</button>
        <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
          <a href="#produto-pessoas-credito">Crédito Estruturado</a>
          <a href="#produto-clt-inss">CLT / INSS</a>
          <a href="#produto-garantia-locaticia">Garantia Locatícia</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="#investidores">Investidores</a>
      <a href="#contato" class="nav-btn">Contato</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main>

<section class="hero" id="inicio">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="hero-brand-lockup">
        <div class="hero-ardire" id="ardireRef">ARDIRE</div>

        <div class="hero-capital" id="capitalRef">
          <span>C</span>
          <span>A</span>
          <span>P</span>
          <span>I</span>
          <span>T</span>
          <span>A</span>
          <span>L</span>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-subtitle">
          SECURITIZAÇÃO E ESTRUTURAÇÃO<br>
          DE ATIVOS DE CRÉDITO
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>
        Atuação institucional em recebíveis, estruturação financeira, análise de crédito, cobrança e soluções empresariais com governança, método e segurança operacional.
      </p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="https://wa.me/5516981266908" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Fale com um consultor</a>
        <a href="#produtos" class="btn btn-secondary">Conheça nossos produtos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-light" id="sobre">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    <div class="text reveal">
      <div class="section-title">
        <div class="eyebrow">Sobre a ARDIRE</div>
        <h2>Estrutura corporativa especializada em crédito, recebíveis e soluções financeiras.</h2>
      </div>

      <p>A ARDIRE Capital atua na estruturação, aquisição e gestão de ativos de crédito, com foco em recebíveis empresariais, antecipações e operações financeiras estruturadas, operando com rigor técnico, governança e disciplina na alocação de capital.</p>
      <p>A ARDIRE Soluções é responsável pela originação, desenvolvimento de relacionamento e estruturação operacional das operações, incluindo análise cadastral e de risco, formalização, gestão de carteira, cobrança e recuperação de ativos.</p>
      <p>Sua atuação abrange operações de crédito para pessoas físicas e jurídicas por meio de parceiros financeiros autorizados, antecipação de recebíveis, além de soluções estruturadas como garantia onerosa em contratos específicos.</p>
      <p>A segregação entre as estruturas assegura maior clareza operacional, mitigação de riscos e alinhamento às melhores práticas de mercado.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-image reveal"></div>
  </div>
</section>

